{"tid":2112060,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解放軍拒撤出山區 中印再陷緊張","createTime":"2020-07-17T04:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T03:33:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5d3168dd1803c8bab7e0f0adf168fab2f125600c","tid":2112060,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:39:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200717/TTQ2BBAEREYJSSFIVCGCFLPQNM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200717%2FTTQ2BBAEREYJSSFIVCGCFLPQNM%2F&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpdRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=9d87ce2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200717%2FTTQ2BBAEREYJSSFIVCGCFLPQNM%2F&h=d856e350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200717/TTQ2BBAEREYJSSFIVCGCFLPQNM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n解放軍拒撤出山區 中印再陷緊張<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ltWkEPJjCBnLV4lFzeJWHcmxck4=/602x390/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2VBMJ62KUZ37VJOI2FIWOC46RU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FltWkEPJjCBnLV4lFzeJWHcmxck4%3D%2F602x390%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2VBMJ62KUZ37VJOI2FIWOC46RU.gif&h=c1d8e83e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中印邊境局勢或再度緊張。印度傳媒引述消息稱，中印最新一輪邊境會談結束，中方拒絕全面撤出班公錯湖（圖）北岸山區，印度高度戒備，增派坦克，嚴防解放軍。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：華府狙擊中國科企 研禁抖音微信<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩軍開會15小時無共識<br />\n<br />\n印度把班公錯湖北岸134公里的刺狀山脊稱為「手指」（finge。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，印方在會晤中向中方表明，雙方若無法做到完全撤軍並且恢復到4月底之前的狀態，這將是不可接受的。目前，雙方已決定監視和核實撤軍過程，直到下周二（21日）至周三（22日）。消息人士說，印度和中國的指揮官將核實前線士兵的相互撤離，以緩解緊張局勢。<br />\n<br />\n《印度時報》/《印度新聞與分析報》"},{"pid":"0318fd05120fe3f1df9fb10a20cbd6b464b4ba7f","tid":2112060,"uid":38904,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cache.hkgolden.media/compress/https://upload.cc/i2/pyKFsH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcache.hkgolden.media%2Fcompress%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FpyKFsH.gif&h=46ba2ad0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cf25a0509c4362674db6ec0d495d8e12c5e3f72","tid":2112060,"uid":98826,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s5enu8v.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs5enu8v.gif&h=edd1ef15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c25233de4a46cfdc92be255ce6090063224110f6","tid":2112060,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:58:45.000Z","msg":"燒山講過中印唔會開戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf11dfb955eb5aa9caeaba9c6b29b832ed405b4","tid":2112060,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:59:12.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16976ed3bd6267ab1792082fe348427d0535e15e","tid":2112060,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:59:22.000Z","msg":"又嚟, 真休沒完沒了"},{"pid":"f7ef3035278524ad2e15e1e057b55a3894e58c5a","tid":2112060,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T05:00:07.000Z","msg":"印度隻空母係咪仲未用得？"},{"pid":"c097650edfee8bf2146f2c74dc937a9133fbe8b2","tid":2112060,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7ef3035278524ad2e15e1e057b55a3894e58c5a","tid":2112060,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T05:00:07.000Z","msg":"印度隻空母係咪仲未用得？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T05:01:23.000Z","msg":"高原點用空母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae35877458dda91